title: HOW DO I RANK UP
body: im trying to try out for a team in the discussions but i am not in a high enough level and i dont know how to rank up in the boards

replies.body:
You probably just needed a quick boards sync, sorry for the confusion DX! 

Posting here will push through a sync if it doesn't happen automatically like it's meant to. Looks like it worked, I can see you as level 30 now!
